Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:21:03.90,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}我們懷著願望入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.29,0:21:11.45,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}夢中的世界被光明照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:18.66,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}滿溢的熱情 寄宿著希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:26.62,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}為了明天暫作休憩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:32.39,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}我們現在在這裡歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.44,0:21:38.24,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}它將在這旅途的終點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:45.35,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}一定會抓住命運的碎片
